    "title": "...but when I'm bad, I'm better.",
    "description": "Always Incendiary. Grants +70% critical hit damage. Moxxi weapon: while held, you gain 2.5% life steal from all damage you deal. Also triggers an unlisted effect on rumble-enabled controllers: continuous vibration while the gun is equipped, even when not firing."
  },
  "notes": "The critical-hit bonus may not appear on the card immediately, but usually shows correctly after restarting. On controllers with rumble, it can cause constant vibration that builds over time. Firing briefly stops the effect, aiming reduces it, and leaving ADS can make it spike. Internally, it is labeled Miss Moxxi's Good Touch, though the prefix can be swapped. If dual-wielded during Gunzerking, the left-hand copy does not trigger the rumble effect.",
